+++  Required packages (Ubuntu):

g++
cmake
libusb-1.0-0.dev
libsdl2-dev
libsdl2-image-dev
libsdl2-ttf-dev
libsdl2-gfx-dev


+++  Download liblightstone, newest version 1.5

Go to https://github.com/openyou/liblightstone
Switch to tag 1.5
Select <> Code -> Download ZIP

cd ..
mv ~/Downloads/liblightstone-1.5.zip ./
unzip liblightstone-1.5.zip
cd liblightstone-1.5
git clone https://github.com/qdot/compily_buildd.git
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make

You might need to bump the CMAKE_MINIMUM_REQUIRED version up
in CMakeLists.txt.


+++  Make

./make.sh


+++  Required privileges:

Read and install

50-wilddivine.rules



+++  User interface

1       Swap top left and top right views
2       Swap top right and bottom left views
3       Swap bottom left and bottom right views
4       Decrease DATA_WIDTH (more data on screen, slower curve)
5       Increase DATA WIDTH (opposite)
6, a, b Toggle audio
0, -    Decrease line width
+       Increase line width
